text: "Young Turks" is a 1981 song by Rod Stewart and taken from his 11th studio album Tonight I'm Yours. It went to number 1 in Israel, number 2 in Canada, number 3 in Australia and number 5 in the United States. == References == Category:1981 songs Category:Rod Stewart songs Category:Synth-pop songs
